ques.p: To ask the hon. Member for North Devon, representing the House of Commons Commission how many television sets are operationally available on the House Estate, broken down by building; and how many such sets are available in hon. Members' offices.

reply.p: The number of annunciator (TV) sets available on the House of Commons estate is as follows:
All Members' offices are fitted with annunciators, and these are included in the aforementioned figures. Records are not kept separately of the number of annunciators which are in Members' offices.
